    "body": "I haven't tested, but from the code it seems to only allow one jump list to exist? I think we should have a design that allow having multiple jump lists, like this:\n\n``` js\n// Set user tasks and custom categories.\napp.setJumpLists({\n  userTask: [ {program, ...}, {program, ...} ],\n  'Custom Category 1': [ {program, ...}, {program, ...} ],\n  'Custom Category 2': [ {program, ...}, {program, ...} ],\n})\n```\n"
