    "created_at": "2016-08-05T14:33:54Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-05T14:33:54Z",
    "body": "I think the following API will cover most use cases:\n\n``` javascript\napp.setJumpList([\n  // 'categoryType' can be either 'frequent' or 'recent',\n  // these are filled in by the OS and list recent or frequent documents\n  { categoryType: 'frequent' },\n  // uncategorized tasks\n  { tasks: [ { program, ... }, { program, ... } ] },\n  // categorized tasks\n  { categoryName: 'Category 1', tasks: [ { program, ... }, { program, ... } ] },\n  { categoryName: 'Category 2', tasks: [ { program, ... }, { program, ... } ] },\n])\n```\n\nProbably also need to provide a wrapper for [`ICustomDestinationList::GetRemovedDestinations()`](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/desktop/dd378401%28v=vs.85%29.aspx) to deal with cases where the end-user explicitly removes items from the jump list.\n\nI'll try to put something together over the weekend.\n"
  },
